J PAUL BROWN
SWARTHMORE, PENNA 1975
ROBERT JOSEPH STEWART
1924-
HUSBAND OF BBS
VISITED THESE GARDENS IN 1944 AS B-17 PILOT
IN EIGHTH USAAF

In memory of 
Barbara Brown Stewart
1927-1992
of Wenonah, New Jersey USA
daughter of J.Paul Brown
she loved these gardens"Ą
▓In memory of a fabulous
Husband, father, writer and pal
Alan Burgess
Greatly missed by wife Anna and children Anya and luke 
He enjoyed a far few swallies 
In this fair city"╣
